rows.label: qst105708_msg0001
rows.name:
Why friends hang around and talk to
Zadazan? Hurry and meet with Don!

rows.label: qst105708_msg0002
rows.name:
Zadazan wait gleefully here
for demise of friends!

rows.label: qst105708_msg0101
rows.name:
Friends stand no chance
against might of Don!

rows.label: qst105708_msg0202
rows.name: All is lost! Lindwurm ruined forever!
